#: ../../source/basic/quick-start.rst:3 c7e1bd4d59de461c94b82937b309696d
msgid "Quick-Start"
msgstr "快速开始"

#: ../../source/basic/quick-start.rst:5 1c3c54e57e654ac695f99c405eb8b6ca
msgid ""
"Let's see a longer example to learn some of the methods that the library "
"has to offer. These are known as \"friendly methods\", and you should "
"always use these if possible."
msgstr ""
"让我们来看一个更长的例子，以便学习一下库所提供的方法。"
"这些方法被称为 \"友好方法\"，你应该会总是使用它们的。"

#: ../../source/basic/quick-start.rst:81 33ec021b46f4454d921cb70370d1cc94
msgid ""
"Here, we show how to sign in, get information about yourself, send "
"messages, files, getting chats, printing messages, and downloading files."
msgstr ""
"上面的例子展示了如何进行登录、获取个人信息、发送消息、文件、参与聊天、打印消息以及下载文件。"

#: ../../source/basic/quick-start.rst:85 2305b02eda604b84911e4623b1aea973
msgid ""
"You should make sure that you understand what the code shown here does, "
"take note on how methods are called and used and so on before proceeding."
" We will see all the available methods later on."
msgstr ""
"在继续之前，您务必要确保自己理解此处所展示的代码的作用，明白方法是如何被调用和使用的等等。"
"稍后我们会介绍所有可用的方法。"

#: ../../source/basic/quick-start.rst:91 32e28252322c41bcaff06117b6101cd5
msgid ""
"Note that grammers is an asynchronous library, and as such, you should "
"get used to it and learn a bit of basic `asyncio`. This will help a lot. "
"As a quick start, this means you generally want to write all your code "
"inside some ``async def`` like so:"
msgstr ""
"请注意，grammers 是一个异步库，因此您需要习惯使用它，"
"并学习一些基本的 `asyncio` 知识。这将非常有帮助。"
"作为快速入门，你可以简单的理解成，"
"只需要将所有代码都写在用 ``async def`` 声明的函数内部就可以了："
